name: GMYK
description:
GMYK is a photo of the magnets on my refrigerator, rearranged to give myself the friendly reminder in the fun CMYK palette. Personally, it is an experiment with flash, my recent lens purchase, and a bit of an exploration of typography/color palettes. CMYK to me is high-energy and positive, the whole point of GM. 

All proceeds from this token will go right back into the Tezos community, and holders will be offered benefits such as early/exclusive access to content in the future... sometimes in exchange for the token! The goal is to keep the GM's going around. All that being said, I appreciate each and every one of you and your support :)
